OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784623688
OL,3,CSir Chris Bryant appointed as Northern
OL,4,CIreland Secretary
OL,6,FSir Chris Bryant has been appointed to
OL,7,Fserve as the new Secretary of State
OL,8,Ffor Northern Ireland.
OL,10,FThe Rhondda and Ogmore MP and former
OL,11,Fminister for trade and labour was
OL,12,Fannounced by Prime Minister Andy
OL,13,FBurnham during a long-running process
OL,14,Fto appoint his Cabinet.
OL,16,FThe announcement came just after 11pm
OL,17,Fon Monday after it emerged earlier
OL,18,Fthat Hilary Benn would not be
OL,19,Fcontinuing in the role.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
