PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784623688
OL,3,CSir Chris Bryant appointed as Northern
OL,4,CIreland Secretary
OL,6,FMr Benn pledged to support Mr Burnham
OL,7,Ffrom the backbenches as he confirmed
OL,8,Fhe would be leaving the position.
OL,10,FThe Labour veteran had been serving
OL,11,Fsince he was appointed by former
OL,12,Fpremier Sir Keir Starmer after their
OL,13,Fparty came back into power in 2024.
OL,15,FMr Benn was the first person from
OL,16,FLabour in the role in 14 years, since
OL,17,Fthe party lost the 2010 general
OL,18,Felection.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
