PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784623688
OL,3,CSir Chris Bryant appointed as Northern
OL,4,CIreland Secretary
OL,6,FIrish Minister for Foreign Affairs
OL,7,FHelen McEntee paid tribute to Mr Benn
OL,8,Fas having "brought warmth and a
OL,9,Fconstructive approach to all of his
OL,10,Frelationships here in Ireland".
OL,12,FDUP leader Gavin Robinson paid tribute
OL,13,Fto Mr Benn as an "honourable man".
OL,15,FHe told media in Belfast that while he
OL,16,Fhad "difficulties" with Mr Benn's
OL,17,Fposition on the legacy of Northern
OL,18,FIreland's troubled past, he recognised
OL,19,Fhe had put "a lot of his time and
OL,20,Feffort" into trying to tackle that
OL,21,Fissue.
