OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784623688
OL,3,CSir Chris Bryant appointed as Northern
OL,4,CIreland Secretary
OL,6,FLater on Monday, Mr Benn announced he
OL,7,Fwas leaving the role in a statement on
OL,8,Fsocial media platform X.
OL,10,FHe described the "great privilege" to
OL,11,Fhave served, and also pledged his
OL,12,Fsupport for Mr Burnham.
OL,14,F"It has been a great privilege to
OL,15,Fserve as Secretary of State for
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland and to work with the
OL,17,Fmany wonderful people I have met over
OL,18,Fthe last 2 years," he wrote.
OL,26,@rD@ROUrD@bO]vD@AOUzD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
