PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784623688
OL,3,CSir Chris Bryant appointed as Northern
OL,4,CIreland Secretary
OL,6,F"I wish my successor all the very best
OL,7,Fin working with the Executive to
OL,8,Fprotect stability, continuing to
OL,9,Fgenerate growth and investment and in
OL,10,Ftaking forward the Troubles Bill which
OL,11,Fis so important for so many families.
OL,13,F"The Prime Minister will have my full
OL,14,Fsupport from the backbenches."
OL,16,FIn a statement Ms McEntee thanked Mr
OL,17,FBenn for his "deep commitment to
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland, and to the UK-
OL,19,FIreland relationship more broadly".
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUvD@^O]yD@NOU{D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
