OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784623688
OL,3,CSir Chris Bryant appointed as Northern
OL,4,CIreland Secretary
OL,6,F"He approached his role with purpose
OL,7,Fand understanding, and with a clear
OL,8,Fwish to make things better for all the
OL,9,Fpeople of Northern Ireland," she said.
OL,11,F"That approach was what allowed both
OL,12,Four governments to reach agreement
OL,13,Flast September on the Joint Framework
OL,14,Fon the Legacy of the Troubles, the
OL,15,Ffirst such comprehensive agreement on
OL,16,Fthe issues in more than a decade.
OL,18,F"The framework puts victims, survivors
OL,19,Fand families at its heart."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@\O]sD@AOUzD@AOU{D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
