PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784623688
OL,3,CSir Chris Bryant appointed as Northern
OL,4,CIreland Secretary
OL,6,FMs McEntee added: "Hilary has brought
OL,7,Fwarmth and a constructive approach to
OL,8,Fall of his relationships here in
OL,9,FIreland, and indeed in Northern
OL,10,FIreland.
OL,12,F"I wish Hilary the very best in the
OL,13,Ffuture.
OL,15,F"I look forward to working with his
OL,16,Fsuccessor in the time ahead."
OL,18,FMr Robinson also said he looked
OL,19,Fforward to engaging with the next
OL,20,FNorthern Ireland Secretary.
OL,26,@nD@SOUtD@AOUwD@AOUxD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
