PN,41208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784623688
OL,3,CSir Chris Bryant appointed as Northern
OL,4,CIreland Secretary
OL,6,F"I thank Hilary Benn for his service
OL,7,Fas Secretary of State for Northern
OL,8,FIreland and wish him well for the
OL,9,Ffuture," he said in a statement on
OL,10,FMonday evening.
OL,12,F"While we have had significant
OL,13,Fdisagreements on a number of important
OL,14,Fissues, particularly legacy, the
OL,15,FWindsor Framework and the need for
OL,16,FGovernment to act more decisively in
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland's interests, those
OL,18,Fdifferences were always advanced
OL,19,Frobustly and respectfully.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@HO]tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784623688
OL,3,CSir Chris Bryant appointed as Northern
OL,4,CIreland Secretary
OL,6,F"The office of Secretary of State
OL,7,Fcarries immense responsibility, and
OL,8,Fwhoever succeeds Mr Benn must
OL,9,Frecognise the importance of working
OL,10,Fconstructively with all parties whilst
OL,11,Fworking to strengthen Northern
OL,12,FIreland's place within the United
OL,13,FKingdom, and the need to deliver
OL,14,Fstable, accountable government that
OL,15,Fdelivers the best services and
OL,16,Foutcomes for our people here.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
