PN,41210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784623688
OL,3,CSir Chris Bryant appointed as Northern
OL,4,CIreland Secretary
OL,6,F"The Democratic Unionist Party looks
OL,7,Fforward to engaging positively with
OL,8,Fthe incoming Secretary of State in the
OL,9,Finterests of all the people of
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland."
OL,12,FSDLP leader Claire Hanna said while
OL,13,Fshe "did not always agree" with Mr
OL,14,FBenn she "found him to be thoughtful,
OL,15,Fengaged and willing to listen".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@RO]uD@EOUuD@ZO]vD@JOUwD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
