FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784623688
OL,3,CSir Chris Bryant appointed as Northern
OL,4,CIreland Secretary
OL,6,F"That approach stood in marked
OL,7,Fcontrast to some previous secretaries
OL,8,Fof state, and I appreciated his
OL,9,Fwillingness to reckon seriously with
OL,10,Fthe challenges facing Northern
OL,11,FIreland," she said.
OL,13,F"We will be pressing the new Secretary
OL,14,Fof State to ensure momentum is
OL,15,Fmaintained on institutional reform,
OL,16,Fsustainable public finances and the
OL,17,Flong-term stability of Northern
OL,18,FIreland's political institutions."
